[CONNECTION ESTABLISHED]

“Thank you for coming. Proceed with your jo-”

“Don't give me that! What do you really want to tell me? What can I do to help you? Please, tell me! What happens when I continue with this job?”

[CONNECTION CLOSED]

What am I doing… I'm only putting these people in danger by asking questions, and yet I still try, for my own selfish reasons. Why would they even be able to provide me the answers I seek?
